<div class="com-share" data-id="11869" data-title="《新版支付宝，真的不是“支付宝+大众点评+微信”的三合一应用么？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11869/medium/11869.jpg?1436636016" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11869.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
